{"tid":690772,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救！！！] 錢七漏水情況嚴重，經常水溫過高行唔到車","createTime":"2018-06-05T06:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T09:34:20.000Z","uid":106512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4dd696122a557a78f8d0f415b84948c59a7d273","tid":690772,"uid":106512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"話說屋企就有架06年出廠既日產錢七，早兩個星期就試過行行下車水溫太高就被迫停車，當時就拎過去車房check過話冇明顯問題，只係水箱冇水。<br />\n<br />\n咁嗰次之後都有用車有check開水箱水位，但就到最近發現入完水之後，就算未撻車都會漏到成地都係水，撻左車之後就漏得仲勁但副水箱又冇少到水，基本上想再用車都已經係冇可能。<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位巴打，呢啲情況多數係主水箱有問題，定係已經波及到引擎既冷卻系統？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d51d346167caa6cef5bd3f17ff226827523718","tid":690772,"uid":106512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"想知道如果真係要整既話大約要幾錢?<br />\n好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129f190a1b86975c15dbdaa8c2a8a39e7c9e5b44","tid":690772,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"水箱漏水咪試邊度漏，換件囉<br />\n<br />\n再唔整就燒簪口成部扔得"},{"pid":"6f5c85012edb655c8c5523ef8e8eb0e8c829afb7","tid":690772,"uid":19715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"睇下 上下水喉有冇穿 <br />\n同埋水箱入面d水有冇變奶茶 如果有麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c3f56d596b3619710d25a2c499f88058c24e26","tid":690772,"uid":771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"冇錢唔好學人養車，養車就要預錢維修保養"},{"pid":"7918c61372a4059011e8e0406b1bdd10a274a1b1","tid":690772,"uid":106512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c3f56d596b3619710d25a2c499f88058c24e26","tid":690772,"uid":771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"冇錢唔好學人養車，養車就要預錢維修保養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T09:14:03.000Z","ms